<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Bulk Import Data</h1>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Import Instructions</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Upload a CSV file with the following columns:</p>
    
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2 mb-4">
      <li><strong>owner_name</strong> (required) - Username for the owner</li>
      <li><strong>email</strong> (optional) - Owner's email address</li>
      <li><strong>serial_number</strong> (optional) - Serial number of the computer</li>
      <li><strong>computer_model</strong> (optional) - Computer model name</li>
      <li><strong>condition</strong> (optional) - Condition of the computer</li>
      <li><strong>run_status</strong> (optional) - Run status of the computer</li>
      <li><strong>description</strong> (optional) - Component description</li>
      <li><strong>component_type</strong> (optional) - Type of component</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">You can include multiple rows for the same owner to add multiple computers and components. If owner_name already exists, it will be linked to that owner.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
    <%= form_with url: admin_bulk_uploads_path, method: :post, local: true, multipart: true, class: "space-y-4" do |form| %>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
          CSV File
        </label>
        <%= form.file_field :file, accept: ".csv", required: true, class: "block w-full text-sm text-gray-500 file:mr-4 file:py-2 file:px-4 file:rounded file:border-0 file:text-sm file:font-semibold file:bg-blue-50 file:text-blue-700 hover:file:bg-blue-100" %>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Max file size: 10MB</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-4 flex gap-3">
        <%= form.submit "Import Data", class: "bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded font-medium hover:bg-blue-700" %>
        <%= link_to "Cancel", admin_owners_path, class: "bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 px-4 py-2 rounded font-medium hover:bg-gray-300" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
    <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Example CSV Format:</h3>
    <pre class="text-xs text-blue-800 overflow-x-auto">owner_name,email,serial_number,computer_model,condition,run_status,description,component_type
john_doe,john@example.com,SN-001,Dell XPS 13,Good,Running,RAM 8GB,Memory
john_doe,john@example.com,SN-001,Dell XPS 13,Good,Running,SSD 512GB,Storage
jane_smith,jane@example.com,SN-002,MacBook Pro,Excellent,Running,GPU,Graphics</pre>
  </div>
</div>
